warehouseQuery.query:
SELECT r_object_id
       , i_position
       , name
       , value
 FROM gpdip_prd.gpdip_uddl_regulatory.gdms_coredatasheet_repeating 
 where name in ('PFLEET_SUB_COUNTRY_ROW_ID','R_VERSION_LABEL');

SELECT r_object_id
       , i_position
       , name
       , value
 FROM gpdip_prd.gpdip_uddl_regulatory.gdms_prescribinginfo_repeating
 where name in ('PFLEET_SUB_COUNTRY_ROW_ID','R_VERSION_LABEL');

SELECT r_object_id
       , i_chronicle_id
       , object_name
       , title
       , xm_status
       , i_has_folder
       , subtype
       , xm_language
 FROM gpdip_prd.gpdip_uddl_regulatory.gdms_coredatasheet_single
WHERE i_has_folder = 1

expression.expression: (ARRAY_TO_STRING(ARRAY_AGG(CAST(VALUE AS string) ORDER BY CAST(VALUE AS string)), ','))

warehouseQuery.query:
SELECT app_country_id
       , country_name
       , country_abbreviation
       , product_name
       , is_static
       , is_active
       , extract_date
 FROM gpdip_prd.gpdip_uddl_regulatory.pfleet_country
WHERE parent_app_country_id is not null and is_active = 1

expression.expression: (ARRAY_TO_STRING(ARRAY_AGG(CAST(VALUE AS string) ORDER BY CAST(VALUE AS string)), ','))
